query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.role, u.organizationId, o.name as orgName 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN organizations o ON u.organizationId = o.id 
WHERE u.email LIKE '%niaghi%' OR u.email LIKE '%proagentur%';
